query:
SELECT s.id, s.siteNumber, s.mapMarkerX, s.mapMarkerY, s.floorLevelId, fl.levelName, fl.mapImageUrl
FROM sites s
LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON s.floorLevelId = fl.id
WHERE s.centreId = (SELECT id FROM shopping_centres WHERE name LIKE '%Highlands%' LIMIT 1)
ORDER BY s.siteNumber;
